# Rules Auditor

When the user says **"run auditor"**, **"audit rules"**, or **"check compliance"**, invoke the **rules-auditor** skill at `.cursor/skills/rules-auditor/SKILL.md`.

The skill handles the full audit process: loading all rules, scanning every file, reconciling `TECHDEBT.md`, and reporting findings.

## TECHDEBT.md Quick Reference

- Lives at the repo root — NEVER inside a package
- Items MUST be removed when fixed — NOT a changelog
- Sorted by priority (P0 first, P3 last)
- Empty sections MUST be omitted
- If zero items remain, delete the file entirely
